{"tid":1681531,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"人人都係音樂家 《願榮光歸香港》","createTime":"2019-10-29T13:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T15:40:36.000Z","uid":333082,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8ed87e048ca6a22efbce684c763bf01e44efc51b","tid":1681531,"uid":333082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:16:31.000Z","msg":"記得細個嗰時吹牧童笛，吹lun 到走曬音，比呀媽hi 我叫我唔好再吹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連第二日要考試都唔俾我吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 叫我落街吹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等無人喺屋企嗰時先吹又比隔籬鄰舍大叫 &quot;唔好嘈啦！&quot;  有時連隔離屋隻狗都吠我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我並唔同意佢哋嘅講法，走音唔一定係難聽<br />\n我從來沒有放棄成為一個偉大音樂家嘅夢想 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自從各區出現商場大合唱，見到d巴打絲打隨手攞起支長笛/小提琴/打鼓又有乜都有<br />\n好似連夾都唔使夾就變咗管弦樂團<br />\n簡直熱情奔放 創意無限<br />\n燃點起我心中嘅一團火<br />\n係呢個moment 要爆喇<br />\n<br />\n自製左一個願榮光歸香港音樂盒<br />\n今次應該唔會再比呀媽hi 同比狗吠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MViSZmyywGI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMViSZmyywGI&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg7Xqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=c82cecdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MViSZmyywGI</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n香港人加油<br />\n各位11月2號維園見</span>"},{"pid":"4ed780deda48e192be29ebc4be2ca82db30e0776","tid":1681531,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Mfv693.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Mfv693.jpg&h=975a7fc9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtm3RDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtm3RDU.jpg&h=fd9c9c47&s={SIZE}\" />